  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But as I said, per-- until, the only time-- well, you know, our school had-- was a regular gymnasium then, but they did not have the right to-- to give you the [? baklava, ?] to give you the [? matora. ?] So we were five or six of us.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One-- two of them are both girls also in this picture too, [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Shatya ?] and [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Shalayvan. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were-- we were supposed to take our exams in a gymnasium called [?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Pinikap ?], which was a boy's gymnasium, and when we came there, this was-- and of course we got, you know, the instructions, they wanted to do-- and this was the only time that we-- that we-- because they came to us, one or two of the men, because this was a Polish [INAUDIBLE] gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, there was no college education in any-- at any rate.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they said to us-- one said to me-- if you are going to help me-- whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Chemistry, I don't remember, or calculus.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't think I remember any more.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I wouldn't remember what I did anyway.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he said, I will help you with Polish literature.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I got so offended, because I really-- we were very, very well prepared.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Considering the fact that we were Jews, we were good students.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So-- and then, when I wrote my-- you know, there was always a written test, and then they would come and do the oral test.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I came to the oral test-- and you don't know Polish literature, it wouldn't make any difference.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Kashinski ?] writer.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
